Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.36,0:23:00.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}I want to remain like this for just a little bit longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.19,0:23:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}Every time we touch, my heart skips a beat.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.96,0:23:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}I think of you more than anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.97,0:23:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}I want you so much I could melt.
